<p>light in the station and the lamp glasses are painted black.<br/>At 10.30pm we arrived at Tedworth. Then we had a four mile march to Park-house Camp Salisbury Plain.<br/>Arriving there about 12 midnight.<br/>We were kept out in the cold till nearly 2am as they had not arranged for our coming. Then we had to be issued with blankets (four).</p>
